Taxi, Don Kar Taxi, Drakkar Taxi, Driver Pro Taxi, Dubai Taxi, Dur Taxi, Electro Taxi, Energy Taxi, Express Taxi, Fergana City Taxi, Final Go Taxi, Final Taxi, Firdavs Taxi, Forever Taxi, Fresh Globus Taxi, Garaj Taxi, Globus Taxi, Good Car Servis Taxi, GTA Drive Taxi, GTA Taxi, Guliston Leader Taxi, Hamkor Taxi, Home Delivery Taxi, Inter Taxi, Ishonch Taxi, Kapital Express Taxi, Kapital Taxi, King Taxi, Komfort Taxi, Kushon Taxi, Leader NKS Taxi, Legenda Taxi Nks, Legenda Urgench Taxi, Lider Taxi, Like Taxi, Line Taxi 77, LION SHER, Lite Taxi, Luxe Taxi, Lyuks Taxi, Makon Taxi, Malibu Taxi, Mandarin Taxi, Maroqand TaxiДоставка, Maroqand Taxi, MasterDelivery Taxi, Master Delivery, MD Taxi, MEGA TAXI, Mexroj Real Taxi, Muslim Pro Taxi, Muslim Taxi, Mustang Taxi, Nomer 1 Taxi, Novza Taxi, Nukus Comfort Go Taxi, Orzu Taxi, PartnerLeader Taxi, Pickup Taxi, PLS Delivery Taxi, PLS Taxi, Polaris Deliver, Polaris Group Taxi, Premial Taxi, Premier Taxi, PREMIUM 24 Taxi, Premium Taxi, Prestige Taxi, Profi Taxi, Pro Taxi Доставка, Pro Taxi, Puldor Premium Taxi, Raketa Taxi Namangan, Raketa Taxi Tashkent, Ravon Taxi, Red Taxi, Registan Taxi, Rich Taxi, Sakina Taxi, Sevimli Taxi Go, Shark Taxi, Sharq Taxi, Shef Taxi Andijon, Shef Taxi, Sherxan Taxi, Silk Road Taxi, Sofiya Lucky Taxi, Solar Taxi, Soyuz Taxi, Star Taxi, SULTAN TAXI BUKHARA, SULTAN TAXI SAMARKAND, SULTAN TAXI TASHKENT, TashMediaTrans Taxi, Taxi Halol, Telex Taxi, Tesla Taxi, Tezkor Taxi, TiFa Доставка, TiFa, Tonggi Parvoz Taxi, Top Taxi, Unique Taxi, Universal Taxi, Urban Taxi, Uzum Taxi, Vatan Group Taxi, Vatan Taxi, VIP Taxi, Xalqona Taxi, Xizmat Taxi, Yasrib Taxi, Yengil Taxi, YURTA TAXI, Zamon Taxi, Zolotoy Brand Taxi, Zoom Logistic Taxi, Zoom Taxi, СDB Express Taxi, Такси люкс 2023, Такси Люкс Доставка.</span><br><span style=\\\"color:hsl(0,0%,30%);\\\"><u>PAYMENT AGGREGATION SYSTEMS (QIWI UZBEKISTAN)</u> - to\'lov tizimi, Qiwi koshelek-da ro\'yxatdan o\'tish vaqtida mijozlarga SMS-xabar berish;</span><br><span style=\\\"color:hsl(0,0%,30%);\\\"><u>Payway Taxi,Polaris Delivery</u>;</span><br><span style=\\\"color:hsl(0,0%,30%);\\\"><u>«QUICK PAYMENTS SOLUTION» MChJ</u> (QPS), www.quickpay.uz) - to\'lov tizimi, mijozlarga SMS xabar berish, to\'lovlarni tasdiqlash kodlarini yuborish;</span><br><span style=\\\"color:hsl(0,0%,30%);\\\"><u>Road 24/7</u> («AUTODOC» MChJ, STIR: 309681777, web-сайт vamobililovasi - ishlab chiqilmoqda); SafeRoad - O\'zbekiston Respublikasi Yo\'l harakati xavfsizligi davlat inspeksiyasi tomonidan jarimalar va boshqa xizmatlarni monitoring qilish va to\'lash bo\'yicha xizmatlarni olish uchun onlayn dasturiy platforma (iOS/android).&nbsp;</span><br><span style=\\\"color:hsl(0,0%,30%);\\\"><u>«Smart Soft Development» MChJ</u> - Mijozlarni SMS orqali xabardor qilish, avtorizatsiya kodlarini olish va «Mening yo`nalishim» mobil ilovasi foydalanuvchilarini identifikatsiya qilish.</span><br>«SMARTBOX ENTERPRISE SOLUTIONS» MChJ (STIR: 306765340)<br>web-sayt: https://jobster.uz/<br><a href=\\\"https://ishgo.uz/\\\">https://ishgo.uz/</a><br>Jobster – xodimlarni tanlash jarayonini avtomatlashtirish tizimi.<br>ishGO – sun’iy intellekt qo‘llab-quvvatlanadigan milliy rekruting ekotizimi. Ushbu xizmat O‘zbekistonda ish topish va xodimlarni tanlashga yordam beradi.<br><span style=\\\"color:hsl(0,0%,30%);\\\">«Mening yo`nalishim» - Toshkent shahrida real vaqt rejimida harakatlanish, jamoat transporti (avtobuslar)ning yetib kelish vaqti haqida maʼlumot, eng yaxshi yoʻnalishni tanlash, vaqtni tejash;</span><br><span style=\\\"color:hsl(0,0%,30%);\\\"><u>O\'zim</u> - yakka tartibdagi tadbirkor sifatida ro\'yxatdan o\'tmoqchi bo\'lgan yoki ro\'yxatdan o\'tmoqchi bo\'lgan shaxslar uchun ariza. O\'zim bir necha bosqichda Soliq tizimida yakka tartibdagi tadbirkor bo\'lish imkonini beradi. Bizning ilovamiz doimiy QR-kod yoki boshqa foydalanuvchiga hisob-faktura orqali ishingiz uchun to‘lovni olish imkonini beradi. Ro\'yxatdan o\'tish, PIN-kodni o\'zgartirish, hisob-fakturani berish va to\'lovlarni tasdiqlashda foydalanuvchilarga SMS-xabar berish.</span><br><span style=\\\"color:hsl(0,0%,30%);\\\"><u>\\\"Spectrum Collection\\\" MChJ</u> - Banklar, Bozorlar, Sug\'urta kompaniyalari, Mahsulot do\'konlari, Moliya tashkilotlari va boshqalar kabi tashkilotlarga qarzni to\'lash bo\'yicha o\'z mijozlari bilan muloqotda maslahat yordamini ko\'rsatish;</span><br><span style=\\\"color:hsl(0,0%,30%);\\\"><u>“Stoma Service” </u>SMS-xizmati (zamonaviy stomatologiya klinikasi). 22700 xizmat raqamidan mijozlarni shifokor qabuliga SMS-xabardor qilish;</span><br><span style=\\\"color:hsl(0,0%,30%);\\\"><u>«TEZPAY» MCh</u> (www.tezpay.pro) - to\'lov tizimi, mijozlarni shaxsiy kabinetida ro\'yxatdan o\'tishda SMS-xabar berish, to\'lovlarni tasdiqlash kodlarini yuborish;</span><br><span style=\\\"color:hsl(0,0%,30%);\\\"><u>Urban Telecom</u> (\\\"Independent Telecom Innovations\\\" MCHJ) - O\'zbekistonda telekommunikatsiya xizmatlarining yangi provayderi;</span><br><span style=\\\"color:hsl(0,0%,30%);\\\"><u>Wildberries Uzbekistan</u> («WB INT EXPORT» MChJ, https://uz.wildberries.ru) - marketplace (elektron savdo maydonchasi, virtual savdo maydonchasi), SMS-xabarlar - ro\'yxatdan o\'tish, to\'lov, avtorizatsiya paytida abonentlarni xabardor qilish;</span><br><span style=\\\"color:hsl(0,0%,30%);\\\"><u>YandexGo</u> - O\'zbekistonda taksi haydovchisi bo\'lish, web-sayti: yandexgo.uz;</span><br><span style=\\\"color:hsl(0,0%,30%);\\\"><u>YandexPro</u> - O\'zbekistonda taksi haydovchilari uchun axborot xizmati, web-sayt: pro.yandex/signup/uz-ru;</span><br><span style=\\\"color:hsl(0,0%,30%);\\\"><u>Fasten</u> - sayohatlarga buyurtma berish uchun yangi onlayn xizmat, web-sayt: fasten.com/uz_uz, fasten.com/ru_uz;</span><br><span style=\\\"color:hsl(0,0%,30%);\\\"><u>ZPLAT</u> («ZPLAT»MChJ, www.zplat.uz) - to\'lov tizimi, mijozlarga SMS xabar berish, to\'lovlarni tasdiqlash kodlarini yuborish.</span></td><td><span style=\\\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:hsl(0,0%,30%);\\\">«AURUM STELLA 05» MChJ</span></td></tr><tr><td><span style=\\\"color:hsl(0,0%,30%);\\\"><strong>№55775:</strong></span><br><span style=\\\"color:hsl(0,0%,30%);\\\">0 so\'m/SMS</span><br><span style=\\\"color:hsl(0,0%,30%);\\\">SMS-xabar berish</span></td><td><span style=\\\"color:hsl(0,0%,30%);\\\"><u>«AGROBAZA»</u> SMS-xabarnoma - onlayn-do\'koni </span><a href=\\\"http://www.agrobaza.uz\\\"><span style=\\\"color:hsl(0,0%,30%);\\\">www.agrobaza.uz</span></a><span style=\\\"color:hsl(0,0%,30%);\\\">, mijozlarni mahsulotlarga buyurtma berish holati, yetkazib berish holati, ro\'yhatdan o\'tish uchun vaqtinchalik</span><br><span style=\\\"color:hsl(0,0%,30%);\\\">kodni taqdim etish va boshqalar to\'g\'risida</span><br><span style=\\\"color:hsl(0,0%,30%);\\\">SMS-xabar berishni amalga oshirish. Ilovadan SMS-xabarnomaga obuna bo\'lish abonent tomonidan mustaqil ravishda amalga oshiriladi.</span><br><span style=\\\"color:hsl(0,0%,30%);\\\">Internet-portaldan SMS-xabarlarni avtomatik yuborish obunasini bekor qilish uchun Abonent Internet-portalga murojaat qilishi kerak.</span><br><span style=\\\"color:hsl(0,0%,30%);\\\"><u>«Glotr.uz»</u> xizmati (www.glotr.uz onlayn savdo markazi) mijozlarga SMS-xabar berish uchun mo\'ljallangan, shuningdek, savdo markazlarining sotuvchilari, mahsulotga buyurtma berish</span><br><span style=\\\"color:hsl(0,0%,30%);\\\">holati, yetkazib berish holati, buyurtma holati,</span><br><span style=\\\"color:hsl(0,0%,30%);\\\">chaqirib olish holati, nashr holati, ro\'yxatga olish uchun vaqtinchalik kodni taqdim etish va boshqalar. Ilovadan SMS-xabarnomaga obuna bo\'lish abonent tomonidan mustaqil ravishda amalga oshiriladi. Internet-portaldan</span><br><span style=\\\"color:hsl(0,0%,30%);\\\">SMS-xabarlarni avtomatik yuborish obunasini bekor qilish uchun Abonent internet-portalga murojaat qilishi kerak.</span><br><span style=\\\"color:hsl(0,0%,30%);\\\"><u>«CLICKMarket»</u> SMS-xabarnoma - onlayn-do\'koni</span><br><a href=\\\"http://www.click.market.uz\\\"><span style=\\\"color:hsl(0,0%,30%);\\\">www.click.market.uz</span></a><span style=\\\"color:hsl(0,0%,30%);\\\">, mijozlarni mahsulotlarga buyurtma berish holati, yetkazib berish holati, ro\'yhatdan o\'tish uchun vaqtinchalik kodni taqdim etish va boshqalar to\'g\'risida SMS-xabar berishni amalga oshirish. Ilovadan SMS-xabarnomaga obuna bo\'lish abonent tomonidan mustaqil ravishda amalga oshiriladi. Internet-portaldan</span><br><span style=\\\"color:hsl(0,0%,30%);\\\">SMS-xabarlarni avtomatik yuborish obunasini bekor qilish uchun Abonent Internet-portalga murojaat qilishi kerak;</span><br><span style=\\\"color:hsl(0,0%,30%);\\\"><u>ioka xizmati</u> - bu aviachiptalarni sotish uchun onlayn platforma (www.ioka.uz). SMS-xabar berish ioka hisobni ochish holati haqida xabar berish, kompaniya veb-saytida avtorizatsiya qilish uchun vaqtinchalik kodni taqdim etish uchun ishlatiladi. SMS-xabarnomaga obuna bo\'lish abonent tomonidan mustaqil ravishda amalga oshiriladi. Veb-saytdan SMS-xabarlarni avtomatik yuborish obunasini bekor qilish uchun Abonent veb-saytga murojaat qilishi kerak. So\'rovlar/hodisalar va javoblar uchun quyidagi variantlar mavjud;</span><br><span style=\\\"color:hsl(0,0%,30%);\\\"><u>InfoZone</u> xizmati SMS-kontentni uzatish uchun kontent-provayder (www.infozone.uz) bo\'lib, o\'z mijozlarini tizimning avtomatlashtirilgan ish joyidagi harakatlar haqida xabardor qiladi.</span><br><span style=\\\"color:hsl(0,0%,30%);\\\">SMS-xabarlarga obuna bo\'lish/obunani bekor qilish abonent tomonidan Info Zone veb-saytiga tashrif buyurgan holda mustaqil ravishda amalga oshiriladi;</span><br><span style=\\\"color:hsl(0,0%,30%);\\\"><u>«QR-online»</u> - QR kodiga asoslangan universal standartlashtirilgan to\'lov xizmati O\'zR Markaziy banki tomonidan tijorat banklari bilan birgalikda ishga tushirildi. Ushbu tizim doirasida savdo-servis korxonalari (xo \'jalik yurituvchi subyektlar) ularga xizmat ko\' rsatuvchi tijorat banklari orqali QR-kodni shakllantiradi va ro \'yxatdan o\' tkazadi. Xaridorlar tovarlar va xizmatlar uchun to\'lovni sotuvchining QR kodini skanerlash va sotib olish miqdorini to\'lov xizmati provayderining mobil ilovasiga kiritish orqali amalga oshiradilar. Ushbu xizmat QR-online tizimining sotuvchisiga to\'lov tafsilotlarini (miqdori, sanasi, vaqti, QR-ID va boshqalar) ko\'rsatgan holda uning QR kodi bo\'yicha amalga oshirilgan bitim to\'g\'risida xabar beradi. Xizmatni ulash / uzish Foydalanuvchining xizmat ko\'rsatuvchi bankiga murojaat qilish orqali amalga oshiriladi.&nbsp;</span><br><span style=\\\"color:hsl(0,0%,30%);\\\"><u>smartcloud.uz</u> («SmartCloud») - bulutli xizmatlar marketpleysi, SMS-xabar berish - kompaniya saytidagi buyurtma holati va hisob ochish holati to\'g\'risida xabar berish, kompaniya saytida avtorizatsiya qilish uchun vaqtinchalik kodni taqdim etish uchun. SMS-ma\'lumotga obuna bo\'lish abonent tomonidan mustaqil ravishda amalga oshiriladi. Veb-saytdan SMS-xabarlarni avtomatik yuborish obunasini bekor qilish uchun Abonent veb-saytga murojaat qilishi kerak.</span><br><span style=\\\"color:hsl(0,0%,30%);\\\"><u>ClickTV</u> - onlayn platformasi (www.clicktv.uz, iOS/Android’dagi ilovalar), shu jumladan filmlar, teleseriallar, sport tadbirlari, yangiliklar va boshqalarni translatsiya qilish uchun;</span><br><span style=\\\"color:hsl(0,0%,30%);\\\"><u>\\\"TOK BOR\\\"</u> kompaniyasi O‘zbekistonda elektr transport vositalarini quvvatlantirish stansiyalarini yetkazib berish, joylashtirish va ularga xizmat ko‘rsatish bilan shug‘ullanadi. Kompaniya foydalanuvchilari kompaniya saytida (tokbor.uz) yoki Tokbor ilovasida (Android, iOS) roʻyxatdan oʻtishlari mumkin. Xizmatga obuna bo\'lish/obunani bekor qilish: SMS-ma\'lumotnomaga obuna bo\'lish/obunani bekor qilish abonent tomonidan Hamkorning veb-sayti yoki ilovasiga murojaat qilish orqali mustaqil ravishda amalga oshiriladi.</span><br><span style=\\\"color:hsl(0,0%,30%);\\\">Shaxsiy hisobingizga kirganingizda SMS yuboriladi.</span><br><u>«UZMB»</u> - O\'zbekiston Respublikasi Markaziy bankining mobil ilovasiga kirishda abonentlarga otr kodlarini yuborish uchun - \\\"Markaz bank mobil ilovasi\\\", unda siz axborot xizmatlari va xizmatlarini olishingiz mumkin – ochiq kartalar va hisoblar soni, identifikatsiya xizmati va boshqalar. Xizmatni ulash/uzish O\'zbekiston Respublikasi Markaziy bankining mobil ilovasini yuklab olish / ishlatish orqali amalga oshiriladi.</td><td><span style=\\\"color:hsl(0,0%,30%);\\\">«INFOZONE» MChJ</span><br><a href=\\\"https://www.infozone.uz/\\\"><span style=\\\"color:hsl(0,0%,30%);\\\">www.infozone.uz&nbsp;</span></a></td></tr></tbody></table></figure><p>&nbsp;</p>\"}', '{\"ru\": null}', '{\"ru\": \"-\", \"uz\": \"-\"}', '{\"ru\": \"-\", \"uz\": \"-\"}', '{\"ru\": null}', '{\"ru\": null}', '{\"ru\": \"sms-informirovanie\", \"uz\": \"sms-malumot-berish\"}', 'images/x1w0TGCGHjyIkmhP8g0a8QEfJTros5dv2QUlI2J1.svg', 'images/3vslqlCBRr8jrpTHcMGhbK8EvyY5RzwGxLmq3oHX.svg', 0, '2022-04-25 19:00:00', NULL, 0);
